<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/10733032/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            王二的经济学故事的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 76 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5458953">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5458953/" class="title-link">经济学爱好者的馒头</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5458953"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhouzixun/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1389797-127.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zhouzixun/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">周先生</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-06-08"
      class="main-meta">2012-06-08 15:50:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5458953_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  作为一个知识爱好者，最可怕的不是没有知识，不是不学无术，不是附庸风雅。最可怕的是偏执。 偏执是知识的“毒药”。因为偏执的最严重后果是扼杀了知识的发展。我曾经非常喜欢一位“经济学者”的作品。他的一本著作被成为通识，“犀利”的文笔，无所 不包的话题。最著名的例子...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5458953/#comments">(34回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">185有用 / 20没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5458953_full" class="hidden">
